{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201", "id": 618361178, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU2MTgzNjExNzg=", "number": 72201, "title": "proc_macro in an existing library crate", "user": {"login": "zbraniecki", "id": 449986, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ0OTk4Ng==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/449986?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki", "html_url": "https://github.com/zbraniecki", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zbraniecki/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2020-05-14T16:18:27Z", "updated_at": "2020-05-14T16:40:08Z", "closed_at": "2020-05-14T16:22:55Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "In multiple crates that I work on, `proc_macro` is used as a performance optimization helper for a parsing library.\r\n\r\nFor example, in case of [`unic_locale`](https://github.com/zbraniecki/unic-locale) I use it to allow users to specify a valid locale identifier at build time with no runtime cost:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nuse unic_locale::{locale, Locale};\r\n\r\nconst loc = locale!(\"en-US\");\r\nconst loc2: Locale = \"en-US\".parse().unwrap();\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe former validates at build time and spits out a pre-computed struct.\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, `proc_macro` brings a pretty high maintenance overhead due to the limitation of lib crates and proc_macro crates being separate.\r\n\r\nIt requires me to maintain `unic_locale_impl` crate, `unic_locale_macro` crate which imports `unic_locale_impl` and `unic_locale` crate which reexports both.\r\n\r\nI'd like to maintain just one lib crate that exposes a proc_macro.", "closed_by": {"login": "jonas-schievink", "id": 1786438, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3ODY0Mzg=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1786438?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonas-schievink", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/72201/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0,